							① The Company uses cookies to store and retrieve the information of users in order to provide individually customized services.<br>
							② A cookie is a small quantity of information sent by the server used in operating a website to the computer browser of a user and can be stored on the hard disk of a computer of the users.<br>
							A. Purpose of Using Cookie: Used for providing information optimized for the users by determining each services visited by the users, the types of visits and usages, popular search terms and the use of secure connections, etc.<br>
							B. Installation, Operation and Refusal of Cookie: May refuse to store the cookie by selecting Tool > Internet Option > Privacy menu from the top section of a web browser.<br>
							C. You may experience difficulty in using a customized service when refusing to store the cookie.<br><br>
						</p>

